          • [ - ] CirdomAkul - member since 18-Sep-15

            @MathCatsFootball You have to consider how a goal is scored. Real Madrid risk way more in their midfield and defensive lines and inevitably they have conceded more. Their defensive and midfield lines have more tasks and responsibility than other top teams. There are teams like Barcelona, PSG, City and many more which they have attackers with certain characteristics, capable of creating and finishing chances on their own. In this case, Real have been relying too much on their full backs and midfielders to do the major things. In short, they have had an attacking line which they only consume and don't create enough chances.
